                            <comment id="16272656" author="pauloricardomg" created="Thu, 30 Nov 2017 13:26:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Currently the scrubber and relocate sstables were relying on the compaction strategy index, so this patches change these operation to use a &lt;tt&gt;DiskBoundaries&lt;/tt&gt; object instead and make &lt;tt&gt;CSM.getCompactionStrategyIndex&lt;/tt&gt; private.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/pauloricardomg/cassandra/tree/3.11-14082&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;3.11 patch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Since this depends on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-13948&quot; title=&quot;Reload compaction strategies when JBOD disk boundary changes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-13948&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-13948&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I will wait until that is committed before setting this as PA.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
